00:01:59.059 --> 00:02:04.209
Now is the right time for you to be learning about this great man for three reasons.

00:02:04.779 --> 00:02:09.539
Firstly, he lived such an interesting, varied, curious life,

00:02:09.709 --> 00:02:12.639
that it’s always the right time to learn about George Orwell.

00:02:13.539 --> 00:02:20.449
Secondly, because he is probably best remembered for his criticisms of totalitarianism, and the past

